    <id>http://invalidusrname.github.com/blog/2012/03/06/history</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The more things change, the more they stay the same.</p>

<pre><code>
$ history 1000 | awk '{a[$2]++}END{for(i in a){print a[i] " " i}}' | sort -rn | head
64 git
59 ./bin/rake
56 ls
53 vim
44 cd
30 gst
20 gp
17 cat
16 rake
13 glog
</code>
</pre>



]]></content>
